data.description: Completely NEW ROOF AND GUTTERS JUST COMPLETED July 2023! This peaceful 4 bedroom with 2 full bathroom, open-split floor plan including a 2 car garage offers exceptional indoor and outdoor space. As you pull into the front drive, you will be in awe of the large Oak Trees that shade the front yard. Fully irrigated. Split bedroom floor plan includes main bedroom separate from the other 3 rooms. Centrally located 15 minutes to Marble Falls and 5 Minutes to Kingsland HEB, doctor's office, restaurants, businesses, post office and shopping. Enjoy the private community park with water access to Lake LBJ. Very LOW HOA dues, $40 annually! Starting with the open kitchen containing granite countertops and all stainless steel appliances with abundance of storage which flows to the dining room. Relax in the grand living room with vaulted ceilings and beautiful fireplace to enjoy this winter. The primary bedroom and private full bath offers a soaking tub, stand up shower, dual vanity, and a walk in closet. All 3 other bedrooms are of great size for an office or your guests. Each room has oversized closets with storage. The additional 4th bedroom is great for the work at home individual, office space. Step outside to the back deck to enjoy the private shaded backyard. Plus a newly built 20x16 storage/workshop in the back yard for all of your lawn equipment, camping gear or holiday decor. Large enough to convert into additional living space or a hobby room.WASHER AND DRYER DO CONVEY!
